"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-world-behind-the-world-review-what-the-brain-scan-misses-6033e7ad?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《世界背后的世界》评论：<strong>大脑扫描遗漏了什么</strong></a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-world-behind-the-world-review-what-the-brain-scan-misses-6033e7ad"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-821062?width=700&amp;height=470" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">史蒂文·西沃特/悉尼先驱晨报/盖蒂图片社</span></div></div></div><p>神经科学家的研究就好像思想和感觉的作用微乎其微。意识无法绘制其流动图。<em>朱利安·巴吉尼评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-world-behind-the-world-review-what-the-brain-scan-misses-6033e7ad?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-fourth-turning-is-here-and-end-times-3439006b?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《第四次转折》和《末世》评论：巨轮</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
